TopicTitle: Modded Game Crashing When Fully Loaded

Articles.Content:
KSP: 0.25 Windows 64

Problem: Deadly Reentry destroys my RAPIER in closed-cycle mode

Ehm... what's the actual problem? The game crashing at start as said in the title or DR killing the Rapier Engine?...

If it's the former, I'd say it's a memory issue. Try starting it with Active Texture Management or the "-force-opengl" attribute.
